Nigerian soul singer Timi Dakolo has fulfilled a bride’s dream of having him as a wedding gift come to reality. <img src="https://notjustok.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/DD11D14A-17A5-4A6F-9853-D4A9DBD3956A-422x420.jpeg"/> The ‘Iyawo mi’ crooner on the 10th of January 2021 via an Instagram post revealed how persistent calls and persuasion from the bride’s husband and her friends made them come up with a plan to surprise the bride. He said; “So I got a call for a wedding in abuja for a lady that just wanted me as her only wedding gift. Unfortunately I had committed to some other gig and the husband and other people kept calling . At some point, we had to come to an agreement, because they refuse to give up. I mean the calls kept coming with the line have you changed your mind ?. So we had to come up with a plan. Let’s wake her up and make her wish come true.Thanks to her colleagues (Planning committee ). Happy married life to OGECHI AND NWACHUKWU EKE. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤"/><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤"/><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤"/><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤"/><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤"/>” View this post on Instagram A post shared by Notjustok.com (@notjustok) Timi Dakolo was recently in the news for performing at 8 different weddings in Abuja on the same day. The post Timi Dakolo Makes A Bride’s Wish Come To Pass appeared first on Most Trusted Voice in Music & Afrobeats from Nigeria & Africa | Notjustok. Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.